# ======================
# Node Connections & Invitations
# ======================

### List connections for a node (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/directory/nodes/{{nodeId}}/connections?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### List connections for a node (sorted by createdAt descending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/directory/nodes/{{nodeId}}/connections?sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Create an invitation (connection request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/directory/nodes/{{nodeId}}/invitations
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetNodeId": {{targetNodeId}},
  "message": "Let's connect our nodes for data exchange"
}

### List invitations for a node (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/directory/nodes/{{nodeId}}/invitations?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### List invitations for a node (sorted by createdAt descending - newest first)
GET {{baseUrl}}/directory/nodes/{{nodeId}}/invitations?sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Accept an invitation (returns credentials)
POST {{baseUrl}}/directory/node-invitations/{{invitationId}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Reject an invitation
POST {{baseUrl}}/directory/node-invitations/{{invitationId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Remove a node connection
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/directory/node-invitations/{{connectionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Rotate credentials for a connection
POST {{baseUrl}}/directory/node-connections/{{connectionId}}/credentials/rotate
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

